Some Properties Calculated by TWOe Relative to AIMInt:
-----------------------------------------------------
  Surf_TWOe(A) = Atomic Surface Method Used for Atom A by TWOe
  Surf_AIMInt(A) = Atomic Surface Method Used for Atom A by AIMInt
